This is one of 6 properties in the Princevalle community that has it's own Driveway! 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 1682 sq ft! This townhouse features 2 large oversized bedrooms both featuring their own balcony. Just a few steps away to the community pool and only a block away to biking/walking  trails and Christmas Hill park!
This location is perfect for walking distance to schools and shopping!
